   117‚Üí## 1.0.2
   118‚Üí
   119‚Üí- Performance
   120‚Üí  - Minor boost (~4%)
   122‚Üí## 1.0.1
   123‚Üí
   124‚Üí- Performance
   125‚Üí  - A significant boost
   127‚Üí## 1.0.0
   128‚Üí
   129‚Üí- Fixed
   130‚Üí  - Raise `TOMLDecodeError` instead of `KeyError` when overwriting implicitly in an inline table
   132‚Üí## 0.2.10
   133‚Üí
   134‚Üí- Fixed
   135‚Üí  - Raise `TOMLDecodeError` if overwriting nested inline tables from the parent inline
   136‚Üí  - Raise `TOMLDecodeError` if escaped Unicode character is not a Unicode scalar value
   137‚Üí- Performance
